{"title_page": "Alvaredo", "text_new": "{{Infobox Portuguese subdivision \n|type = parish \n|official_name      = Alvaredo\n|image_skyline      = \n|image_caption      = \n|image_flag         =\n|image_shield       = \n|image_location     = \n|region             = [[Norte Region, Portugal|Norte]]\n|CIM                = [[Alto Minho]]\n|district           = [[Viana do Castelo District|Viana do Castelo]]\n|municipality       = [[Melga\u00e7o, Portugal|Melga\u00e7o]]\n|coordinates        = {{coord|42.095|-8.303|type:adm1st_region:PT_dim:50000|display=inline,title}}\n|elevation          =\n|area_total         = 4.36\n|population_as_of   = 2011\n|population_total   = 528\n|patron             =\n|area_code          = \n|postal_code        = \n|website            = \n}}\n'''Alvaredo''' is a [[Portugal|Portuguese]] ''[[freguesia]]'' (\"civil parish\"), located in the municipality of [[Melga\u00e7o, Portugal|Melga\u00e7o]].<ref>[http://www.cm-melgaco.pt/portal/page/melgaco/portal_municipal/municipio/municipio_freguesias/Alvaredo C\u00e2mara Municipal de Melga\u00e7o] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110718083129/http://www.cm-melgaco.pt/portal/page/melgaco/portal_municipal/municipio/municipio_freguesias/Alvaredo |date=2011-07-18 }}</ref><ref>[http://www.cm-melgaco.pt/portal/page/melgaco/portal_municipal/municipio/municipio_dadosestatisticos/municipio_estatistica_Demografia Demographics of Melga\u00e7o] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110718083225/http://www.cm-melgaco.pt/portal/page/melgaco/portal_municipal/municipio/municipio_dadosestatisticos/municipio_estatistica_Demografia |date=2011-07-18 }}</ref> The population in 2011 was 528,<ref name=ine>[http://www.ine.pt/ngt_server/attachfileu.jsp?look_parentBoui=165404348&att_display=n&att_download=y Instituto Nacional de Estat\u00edstica (INE)], Census 2011 results according to the 2013 administrative division of Portugal</ref> in an area of 4.36&nbsp;km\u00b2.<ref name=dgt>{{Cite web |url=http://www