, located in the municipality of [[Melga\u00e7o, Portugal|Melga\u00e7o]].<ref>[http://www.cm-melgaco.pt/portal/page/melgaco/portal_municipal/municipio/municipio_freguesias/Alvaredo C\u00e2mara Municipal de Melga\u00e7o] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110718083129/http://www.cm-melgaco.pt/portal/page/melgaco/portal_municipal/municipio/municipio_freguesias/Alvaredo |date=2011-07-18 }}</ref><ref>[http://www.cm-melgaco.pt/portal/page/melgaco/portal_municipal/municipio/municipio_dadosestatisticos/municipio_estatistica_Demografia Demographics of Melga\u00e7o] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110718083225/http://www.cm-melgaco.pt/portal/page/melgaco/portal_municipal/municipio/municipio_dadosestatisticos/municipio_estatistica_Demografia |date=2011-07-18 }}</ref> The population in 2011 was 528,<ref name=ine>[http://www.ine.pt/ngt_server/attachfileu.jsp?look_parentBoui=165404348&att_display=n&att_download=y Instituto Nacional de Estat\u00edstica (INE)], Census 2011 results according to the 2013 administrative division of Portugal</ref> in an area of 4.36&nbsp;km\u00b2.<ref name=dgt>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dgterritorio.pt/cartografia_e_geodesia/cartografia/carta_administrativa_oficial_de_portugal_caop_/caop__download_/carta_administrativa_oficial_de_portugal___versao_2017__em_vigor_/ |title=\u00c1reas das freguesias, concelhos, distritos e pa\u00eds |access-date=2018-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181105172426/http://www.dgterritorio.pt/cartografia_e_geodesia/cartografia/carta_administrativa_oficial_de_portugal_caop_/caop__download_/carta_administrativa_oficial_de_portugal___versao_2017__em_vigor_/ |archive-date=2018-11-05 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n\n[[File:Alvaredo Church.jpg|thumb|200px|left|[[Alvaredo Church]]]]\n\n==Architecture==\n* Chapel of S\u00e3o Br\u00e1s ({{lang-pt|Capela de S\u00e3o Br\u00e1s}})\n* Chapel of S\u00e3o Jo\u00e3o ({{lang-pt|Capela de S\u00e3o Jo\u00e3o}})\n* [[Church of S\u00e3o Martinho (Alvaredo)|